---
import { contacts } from "@/content";
---

<section id="contact" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-cream/50">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-accent mb-5">Записаться</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] mb-8 text-ink">
          Первая консультация — <span class="italic text-accent">бесплатно</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-10">
          30–40 минут разговора. Слушаю задачу, отвечаю на вопросы по&nbsp;рынку,
          ориентирую по&nbsp;срокам и&nbsp;стоимости. Без обязательств.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <a
            href={contacts.whatsapp}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 bg-ink text-paper hover:bg-accent transition group"
          >
            <span class="text-lg">Написать в WhatsApp</span>
            <span class="text-paper group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={contacts.telegram}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 border border-line hover:border-accent transition group bg-paper"
          >
            <span class="text-lg text-ink">Написать в Telegram</span>
            <span class="text-accent group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={contacts.phoneHref}
            class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 border border-line hover:border-accent transition group bg-paper"
          >
            <span class="text-lg tabular-nums text-ink">{contacts.phone}</span>
            <span class="text-accent group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:mt-20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-accent mb-5">Заметки агента</p>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-tight mb-5 text-ink">
          Веду блог о&nbsp;московском рынке
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Разборы сделок, изменения в&nbsp;законодательстве, новостройки,
          практические советы покупателям и&nbsp;продавцам.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <a
            href={contacts.dzen}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center justify-between py-3 border-t border-line text-ink-soft hover:text-accent transition"
          >
            <span>Дзен · Заметки агента</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={contacts.channel}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center justify-between py-3 border-t border-line text-ink-soft hover:text-accent transition"
          >
            <span>Telegram-канал</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={contacts.vk}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center justify-between py-3 border-t border-line border-b text-ink-soft hover:text-accent transition"
          >
            <span>ВКонтакте</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
